{
  "texts": [
    "Listing 9 depicts the prompt.",
    "It consists of a description of the database schema (only tables and columns), the foreign keys and a query in natural language.",
    "After running the clear prompting step of the C3 framework on an example with the Mondial database, Listing 3 shows the prompt generated, which is then submitted to the GPTs models to create the SQL equivalent to the user's NL query.",
    "In lines 4 and 5, only the tables and columns relevant to the user's NL query are provided, following the Table Recall and Column Recall steps.",
    "In line 6, foreign keys are specified, and in line 8 the user's query is presented."
  ]
